            .vacancies__right
              .vacancies__right-about
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title We are happy to meet you if:
                  p.vacancies__right-info • you know how to create strong texts - a qualified copywriter;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • it’s easy to find a common language with those around you - you dispose people to yourself, communicate with them on any topics you need;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • you are well-versed in the intricacies of different PR-tools and understand the benefits of using each, depending on the situation;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • you have experience of successful promotion in social networks, blogs, newsletters and you know the nuances of working with them;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • fluent in English;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • have a high level of self-organization;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • understand the development trends of the Internet market and belong to the digital generation;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • you want to improve in the direction of PR.
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title The big plus will be
                  p.vacancies__right-info • presentation of awards and certificates;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • contacts and media relations;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • termination of higher education in such specialties as PR, journalism, marketing, philology.
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title Part of job responsibilities:
                  p.vacancies__right-info • proposals for strategic PR-development of the company in relation to potential customers and the trade community;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • work on improving the indicator of recognition in the market, maintaining and developing the image of the agency;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • development of a promotion plan for all possible communication channels;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • full promotion of the company's success at thematic events and ratings;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • selection of advertising festivals for participation and sending applications with case studies;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • preparation of speeches by colleagues and agency managers at relevant conferences;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • taking the initiative in conducting information leads;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • development of press releases and publications for promotion in specialized media;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • maintaining activity on the company's social networks (Facebook, VK, Instagram);
                  p.vacancies__right-info • tracking the situation in the media and the behavior of competitors;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • support of PR-campaigns for new projects.
                .vacancies__right-item
                  p.vacancies__right-title Conditions:
                  p.vacancies__right-info • cooperation in the team of one of the best Georgian agencies;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • participation in large and unusual projects;
                  p.vacancies__right-info • decent pay.
